Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.60,0:01:00.94,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji was sent to the other\Nroom after surrendering...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.66,0:01:00.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジは星全部を
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.66,0:01:00.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,安藤と古畑に預けて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.89,0:01:03.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,別室に墜ちた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.94,0:01:02.87,default,,0,0,0,,...all the money and stars to\NAndo and Furuhata.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.26,0:01:07.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,星の売買タイムの時に
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.26,0:01:07.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジに星３つを与え
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.27,0:01:07.54,default,,0,0,0,,They made a firm promise \Nto give 3 stars to Kaiji...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.54,0:01:11.55,default,,0,0,0,,...during the buy-sell time \Nto save him.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.60,0:01:12.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジを救済するという
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.60,0:01:12.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,固い約束を交わす
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.21,0:01:15.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だが いざその時になると…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.24,0:01:14.78,default,,0,0,0,,However, \Nat the crucial moment...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.24,0:01:20.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ダメだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.24,0:01:20.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この星も金も手放さない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.44,0:01:16.64,default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.60,0:01:20.95,default,,0,0,0,,I won't let go of both \Nthe money and stars...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.98,0:01:25.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,放したくない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.98,0:01:25.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,な 何言ってんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.13,0:01:22.56,default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.94,0:01:25.37,default,,0,0,0,,W-What are you saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.69,0:01:27.86,default,,0,0,0,,We can't save \NKaiji if we do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.72,0:01:27.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それじゃカイジさんが
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.72,0:01:27.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,救えないじゃないか
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.75,0:01:32.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,かまわない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.75,0:01:32.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あ… 安藤！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.86,0:01:29.36,default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.70,0:01:31.97,default,,0,0,0,,A... ANDO!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.47,0:01:46.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,土壇場で拒絶 裏切り
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.50,0:01:46.54,default,,0,0,0,,He was rejected and betrayed\Nat the crucial moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.95,0:01:49.67,kaiji-main-top,,0,0,0,,Resurrection
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.61,0:01:53.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何を言う 安藤
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.61,0:01:53.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,バカなこと言うな
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.67,0:01:52.26,default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying, Ando!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.26,0:01:53.59,default,,0,0,0,,Don't say such stupid things!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.65,0:01:57.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうだよ 安藤
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.65,0:01:57.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それじゃあんまりだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.82,0:01:56.82,default,,0,0,0,,That's right, Ando! \NThat's going too far!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.32,0:02:01.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,でも そうしなきゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.32,0:02:01.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺たちだって救われない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.35,0:02:00.83,default,,0,0,0,,But if we don't do that,\Nwe can't save ourselves either.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.19,0:02:05.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,冷静になって よく考えてよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.56,0:02:04.91,default,,0,0,0,,Rationalise and think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.06,0:02:08.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジさんを救ったら
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.06,0:02:08.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺たちに残るのは
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.23,0:02:11.10,default,,0,0,0,,If we're to save Kaiji, we'll only\Nhave 6 million left,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.43,0:02:11.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,３人の金を合わせた600万と
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.03,0:02:14.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今 星を売って得た500万の
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.03,0:02:14.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,1100万だ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.10,0:02:14.44,default,,0,0,0,,and the 5 million we got from\Nselling a star. 11 million in all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.90,0:02:18.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これじゃ大アカなんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.91,0:02:17.01,default,,0,0,0,,We'll be deep in debt!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.48,0:02:21.12,default,,0,0,0,,In fact, both Furuhata and\NI borrowed...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.64,0:02:21.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それに船から借りた軍資金が
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.12,0:02:23.37,default,,0,0,0,,...2 million each \Nfrom the organisers,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.14,0:02:24.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺と古畑さんが200万ずつ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.14,0:02:24.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジさんが1000万
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.37,0:02:24.81,default,,0,0,0,,while Kaiji borrowed 10 million,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.78,0:02:28.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,都合1400万
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.81,0:02:26.92,default,,0,0,0,,which totals to 14 million!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.28,0:02:33.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これだけでもアカなのに
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.28,0:02:33.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さらにこれに４割 金利がつくんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.33,0:02:30.16,default,,0,0,0,,That's enough to be \Nin the red,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.16,0:02:33.23,default,,0,0,0,,and there's the extra \N40% interest too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.49,0:02:37.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,かける1.4で1960
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.49,0:02:37.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,2000万
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.50,0:02:37.00,default,,0,0,0,,Multiplied by 1.4, that's 19.6,\Nclose to 20 million.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.36,0:02:40.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,手持ちの1100じゃ全然足りない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.49,0:02:40.00,default,,0,0,0,,The 11 million \Nwe have is not enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.23,0:02:44.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,900万のアカ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.23,0:02:44.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１人頭300万
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.29,0:02:42.00,default,,0,0,0,,We'll have a debt of 9 million!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.32,0:02:46.57,default,,0,0,0,,Each of us will leave the ship \Nwith a debt of 3 million.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.20,0:02:46.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんな借金背負って
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.20,0:02:46.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,船から降りて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.67,0:02:51.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺たち やり直せるかよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.77,0:02:49.02,default,,0,0,0,,Do you think we can \Nstart over again with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.30,0:02:54.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,古畑さん
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.30,0:02:54.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,シャバに別に借金ないの？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.30,0:02:54.91,default,,0,0,0,,Furuhata, don't you have other\Ndebts out there as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.77,0:02:58.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,え？少し…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.18,0:02:58.16,default,,0,0,0,,A little...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.14,0:03:01.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だったら分かってよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.14,0:03:01.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの人を切って星を売れば
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.16,0:02:59.42,default,,0,0,0,,Then please understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.84,0:03:03.92,default,,0,0,0,,If we take him out, \Nwe'll get a minimum of 15 million!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.55,0:03:04.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,少なくとも あと1500は入る
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.35,0:03:08.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,手持ちの金に
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.35,0:03:08.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それをプラスすれば 2600万
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.42,0:03:08.43,default,,0,0,0,,Adding to what we have, \Nthe total amount is 26 million!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.72,0:03:12.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その上 カイジさんの1000万の
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.72,0:03:12.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,借金は返さなくていい
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.75,0:03:12.23,default,,0,0,0,,It won't matter if Kaiji\Ndoesn't pay back his 10 million.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.59,0:03:16.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺たち２人の船からの借金は
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.59,0:03:16.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,金利を含めても600程度
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.61,0:03:17.01,default,,0,0,0,,Your debt and mine\Ntotal 6 million in all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.96,0:03:20.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,つまり2600引く600で
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.96,0:03:20.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,2000万は浮く
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.01,0:03:20.94,default,,0,0,0,,But after repaying it, we'll\Nget an extra 20 million!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.60,0:03:26.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１人頭1000万
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.60,0:03:26.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺たちは1000万 持って
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.65,0:03:29.08,default,,0,0,0,,We'll get 10 million each...\NThink about it, 10 million each.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.94,0:03:29.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この船から降りられるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.28,0:03:32.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これだけあれば
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.28,0:03:32.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,シャバのケチな借金なんて帳消し
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.32,0:03:32.45,default,,0,0,0,,That'd definitely erase\Nall our debts out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.65,0:03:35.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,違うか？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.76,0:03:34.05,default,,0,0,0,,Am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.35,0:03:40.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ざわ… ざわ… ざわ…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.75,0:03:44.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何言ってるんだ 安藤
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.75,0:03:44.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,てめえ 殺すぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.83,0:03:44.63,default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying, Ando!\NI'll kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.52,0:03:49.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,殺す 殺してやる
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.52,0:03:49.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,古畑 裏切ったらお前も殺す
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.63,0:03:46.06,default,,0,0,0,,I'll kill you! I'll kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.81,0:03:49.07,default,,0,0,0,,Furuhata! If you betray me, \NI'll kill you too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.80,0:03:53.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,フフ 恐れることはない
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.80,0:03:53.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もう二度と あの人と
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.54,0:03:56.07,default,,0,0,0,,What's there to be afraid of?\NWe won't be seeing him again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.53,0:03:56.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,顔を合わせることはないからな
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.47,0:03:59.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,別室にいる連中の
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.47,0:03:59.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この後の境遇は過酷で
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.68,0:03:59.58,default,,0,0,0,,It's believed that those\Nsent to the other room...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.87,0:04:03.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１年もたずに
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.87,0:04:03.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,廃人になるってうわさだ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.96,0:04:03.08,default,,0,0,0,,...will meet a cruel fate and\Nbe rendered useless soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.38,0:04:09.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,すぐに俺たちの顔も忘れるさ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.82,0:04:08.02,default,,0,0,0,,He'll soon forget even\Nour faces.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.72,0:04:15.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,貴様… 貴様！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.72,0:04:15.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,貴様 貴様 貴様 貴様
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.76,0:04:13.32,default,,0,0,0,,Why you! Why you! \NWhy you! Why you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.58,0:04:16.03,default,,0,0,0,,Why you! \NWhy you!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.23,0:04:28.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ぶっ殺す！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.23,0:04:28.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,古畑 安藤を殴れ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.41,0:04:26.14,default,,0,0,0,,I'll kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.14,0:04:30.57,default,,0,0,0,,Furuhata! Beat up Ando! \NBeat him up and save me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.17,0:04:30.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,殴り倒して俺を救え
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.57,0:04:34.00,default,,0,0,0,,Save me, Furuhata!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.57,0:04:34.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,救うんだ 古畑！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.05,0:04:43.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ざわ…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.99,0:04:49.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジさん ごめん
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.19,0:04:49.55,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji... I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.46,0:05:01.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ごめんじゃねえ 古畑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.49,0:05:02.56,default,,0,0,0,,Don't say you're sorry! \NFuruhata, don't apologise!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.03,0:05:06.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,謝ったりするな 謝るな
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.03,0:05:06.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,謝るな 古畑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.56,0:05:05.62,default,,0,0,0,,Don't apologise! \NDon't apologise, Furuhata!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.91,0:05:11.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いいな
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.06,0:05:08.30,default,,0,0,0,,Are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.54,0:05:15.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,星だ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.54,0:05:15.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,500万以上 出せる奴
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.58,0:05:14.79,default,,0,0,0,,Here's a star for anyone\Nwho offers 5 million or more!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.41,0:05:18.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺だ！売ってくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.32,0:05:22.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,よせ よせー！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.55,0:05:20.86,default,,0,0,0,,Stop it! Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.78,0:05:24.56,default,,0,0,0,,The deal was made.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.79,0:05:25.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,売買成立
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.79,0:05:25.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やった！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.73,0:05:29.25,default,,0,0,0,,Alright!\NI got it! I got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.66,0:05:30.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,買った 買ったぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.66,0:05:30.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,買った 買ったー！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.65,0:05:41.65,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji's desire to return...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.70,0:05:41.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジの別室からの生還
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.67,0:05:45.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その願い 計画は破綻
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.82,0:05:45.15,default,,0,0,0,,The realisation that all\Nhis plans are destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.48,0:05:50.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,残るは暗黒だけ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.61,0:05:47.96,default,,0,0,0,,All that's left is \Ndarkness...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.32,0:05:54.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,貴様ら 貴様ら 貴様ら
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.46,0:05:53.65,default,,0,0,0,,Scums! Scums! \NScums!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.19,0:05:57.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それでも人間か
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.28,0:05:57.16,default,,0,0,0,,Can you still call \Nyourselves human?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.09,0:06:01.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ハハハハハ 捨てられて当然
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.71,0:06:01.54,default,,0,0,0,,It's natural to be \Nthrown away like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.49,0:06:07.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,人間 感傷はいっとき
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.49,0:06:07.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,決断は結局 実利に流れる
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.54,0:06:03.49,default,,0,0,0,,We have emotions,\Nbut in reality,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.49,0:06:06.87,default,,0,0,0,,they'll always choose\Nthe most utilitarian way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.07,0:06:09.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,空手では救われるわけがない
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.18,0:06:09.92,default,,0,0,0,,It's only normal that\Na poor man like you...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.97,0:06:12.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,当たり前のこと
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.15,0:06:12.32,default,,0,0,0,,...won't be saved.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.27,0:06:15.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジくん
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.32,0:06:13.17,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.74,0:06:18.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ありがとう
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.74,0:06:18.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ありがとうございます
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.74,0:06:18.52,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you... \NThank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.48,0:06:23.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,必ず… 必ず救い出しますから
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.52,0:06:21.62,default,,0,0,0,,We'll surely...\NWe'll surely save you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.42,0:06:26.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,遠いはずだ あの時
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.52,0:06:25.10,default,,0,0,0,,Of course it felt as if\Nthey were faraway.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.43,0:06:28.89,default,,0,0,0,,I should have realised it\Nat that time!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.35,0:06:29.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,奴らの声を遠く感じて当然
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.76,0:06:34.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,奴らにすれば あの時点で
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.76,0:06:34.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺の命など どうでもいいこと
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.83,0:06:34.43,default,,0,0,0,,I didn't mean anything to them\Nright from the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.63,0:06:39.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの涙は いっときの感傷
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.63,0:06:39.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,決意なき涙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.86,0:06:38.90,default,,0,0,0,,Those tears were just \Nmomentary emotions...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.43,0:06:43.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,腹の底じゃ もう冷酷に
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.43,0:06:43.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,切る算段を始めていた
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.44,0:06:43.24,default,,0,0,0,,They were just \Ncrocodile tears!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.40,0:06:45.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,安藤は100パーセントそう
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.56,0:06:45.70,default,,0,0,0,,Ando must have planned\Nthat from the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.87,0:06:49.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,古畑も無意識下で
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.87,0:06:49.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その作業をしていた
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.91,0:06:49.18,default,,0,0,0,,Furuhata followed the \Nplan without thinking about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.58,0:06:51.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だから遠く感じたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.59,0:06:51.56,default,,0,0,0,,That's why it \Nfelt so insincere...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.64,0:06:55.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの遠さは
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.64,0:06:55.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,奴らの声に現実味が
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.85,0:06:55.38,default,,0,0,0,,That distance was \Nevident in their voices.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.41,0:06:59.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,本気で俺を救おうという意思
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.41,0:06:59.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ぬくもりがなかったんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.56,0:06:59.56,default,,0,0,0,,They never really had the \Nintention to save me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.39,0:07:05.30,default,,0,0,0,,It's too late to \Nrealise that now, Kaiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.42,0:07:05.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,気づくのが遅かったな カイジ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.32,0:07:07.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,友情や口約束でもらえるのは
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.46,0:07:10.18,default,,0,0,0,,Friendships only give you memories\Nand empty promises...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.79,0:07:10.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,旅先からの絵はがきや土産
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.13,0:07:14.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あるいは思い出というガラクタ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.13,0:07:14.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんな程度のもの
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.18,0:07:14.10,default,,0,0,0,,...that amount to \Nnothing at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.50,0:07:16.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,本当に肝心なものは
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.52,0:07:16.83,default,,0,0,0,,There's no way that\Nthe friendship...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.83,0:07:20.10,default,,0,0,0,,...will become something\Ngreat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.84,0:07:20.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,決して友情なんかでは
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.84,0:07:20.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,譲られない
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.84,0:07:23.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,利しかないのさ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.97,0:07:23.01,default,,0,0,0,,It has no value!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.48,0:07:28.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この世で本当に欲しいものや
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.48,0:07:28.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,地位を手に入れようとしたら
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.49,0:07:28.01,default,,0,0,0,,If you really want to gain \Nstatus or possessions,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.25,0:07:30.51,default,,0,0,0,,you'll need money! \NNothing works but money!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.25,0:07:31.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,金！金しかない
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.39,0:07:47.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,結局 お前ら２人は
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.39,0:07:47.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その当たり前の認識が甘かった
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.41,0:07:47.59,default,,0,0,0,,Both of you are too naive \Nto know about the real world.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.37,0:07:50.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺は そのことについてだけは
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.37,0:07:50.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,シビアだったから
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.59,0:07:50.70,default,,0,0,0,,I paid a lot of attention to that,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.64,0:07:53.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こうして生き残れる　まあ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.70,0:07:52.56,default,,0,0,0,,hence I've been able to survive...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.56,0:07:57.01,default,,0,0,0,,Well, do your best to comfort \Neach other from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.21,0:07:57.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あとは せいぜい２人で
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.21,0:07:57.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,慰め合って生きていくんだな
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.22,0:08:09.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,金？救われるには
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.30,0:08:06.30,default,,0,0,0,,Money?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.98,0:08:08.05,default,,0,0,0,,I need money to be saved?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.15,0:08:12.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,金…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.41,0:08:10.37,default,,0,0,0,,Money?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.49,0:08:14.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,利…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.58,0:08:13.59,default,,0,0,0,,Benefits!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.33,0:08:20.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この時 カイジにあるひらめき
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.39,0:08:20.30,default,,0,0,0,,At that moment, \NKaiji had a flash of inspiration!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.57,0:08:23.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジくん？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.61,0:08:22.06,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.74,0:08:29.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おい
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.78,0:08:27.93,default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.05,0:08:41.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,貴様 何をする
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.05,0:08:41.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,離れんか
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.12,0:08:40.65,default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?! \NGet off him!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.76,0:08:53.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,よせ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.76,0:08:53.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,死ぬぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.99,0:08:52.82,default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.82,0:08:55.00,default,,0,0,0,,He'll die! Let him go!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.70,0:08:55.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,離さんか
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.90,0:09:00.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この このガキが
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.00,0:09:01.12,default,,0,0,0,,You stupid punk!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.84,0:09:03.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いい加減にしろ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.12,0:09:02.68,default,,0,0,0,,You should \Nknow your place!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.35,0:09:11.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,このガキ！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.44,0:09:11.20,default,,0,0,0,,You brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.49,0:09:20.77,default,,0,0,0,,Let him go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.49,0:09:21.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,離せ おい
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.60,0:09:30.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前も さっさと出ろ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.60,0:09:30.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,金持って
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.63,0:09:28.07,default,,0,0,0,,Get out of here now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.07,0:09:29.45,default,,0,0,0,,And take your money with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.31,0:09:32.41,default,,0,0,0,,You dumb brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.34,0:09:33.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,このくそガキ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.64,0:09:36.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,見苦しいわ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.64,0:09:36.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,上がれんのは お前の甘さ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.65,0:09:35.07,default,,0,0,0,,Don't you have any sense?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.07,0:09:36.84,default,,0,0,0,,You're unable to \Nget out of here...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.64,0:09:41.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うかつさからだ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.64,0:09:41.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それを いくらねたましいからって
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.84,0:09:37.84,default,,0,0,0,,...because you \Nweren't paying attention!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.08,0:09:42.55,default,,0,0,0,,And you're taking it out on me \Njust because of envy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.11,0:09:46.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺に八つ当たりするとは何事だ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.11,0:09:46.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,クズが
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.55,0:09:44.34,default,,0,0,0,,You piece of trash! \NYou're done for!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.28,0:09:48.02,default,,0,0,0,,Die! Die! Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.32,0:09:49.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,死ね 死ね 死ね
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.32,0:09:49.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前はもう終わりだ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.02,0:09:49.35,default,,0,0,0,,It's the end for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.56,0:09:54.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,生きても あと２～３年
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.56,0:09:54.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,死ね 死にさらせ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.58,0:09:51.98,default,,0,0,0,,You'll have only 2 to \N3 years to live! Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.24,0:09:53.80,default,,0,0,0,,Go and die!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.23,0:10:03.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジくん
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.45,0:10:01.02,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.80,0:10:07.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうして… こんなことをしても
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.80,0:10:07.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何の得にもならないのに
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.93,0:10:07.97,default,,0,0,0,,Why? Nothing will come out \Nof doing such things...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.97,0:10:10.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そりゃ あの男の口様は
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.97,0:10:10.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,悔しいっていうか
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.97,0:10:11.05,default,,0,0,0,,It's true that \Nhis words were vexing,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.91,0:10:14.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,腹立たしかったけど
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.91,0:10:14.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これから先のことを考えたら
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.05,0:10:12.37,default,,0,0,0,,and it makes you mad...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.37,0:10:14.70,default,,0,0,0,,But thinking of \Nwhat's ahead of us,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.31,0:10:16.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,無茶はいけない
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.70,0:10:15.87,default,,0,0,0,,we can't be careless!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.25,0:10:20.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,特に黒服の人への暴力は
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.25,0:10:20.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,心証ってものがあるんだから
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.28,0:10:18.58,default,,0,0,0,,Especially with the guys \Nin black suits around,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.58,0:10:20.88,default,,0,0,0,,it'll reflect badly on us...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.99,0:10:23.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おとなしくしているのが一番
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.16,0:10:23.34,default,,0,0,0,,It's best to obedient.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.32,0:10:26.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,暴れて いいことはひとつもない
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.34,0:10:25.38,default,,0,0,0,,Nothing good will come \Nfrom doing this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.23,0:10:30.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,フッ フフッ そうでもないさ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.54,0:10:28.89,default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.10,0:10:32.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,じたばたすることで開ける
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.24,0:10:32.33,default,,0,0,0,,Only by making \Na last ditch struggle...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.50,0:10:38.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんな活路 逆転 生還
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.58,0:10:33.89,default,,0,0,0,,...can it be opened.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.07,0:10:37.83,default,,0,0,0,,The path to survival...\Nis to struggle.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.30,0:10:41.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そう 生還がある
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.35,0:10:40.40,default,,0,0,0,,There's still a chance\Nto stay alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.84,0:10:43.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まだ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.87,0:10:42.84,default,,0,0,0,,I won't...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.04,0:10:49.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,諦めねえ 最後まで
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.06,0:10:49.56,default,,0,0,0,,I won't give up! \NNot until the very end!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.75,0:11:01.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんな…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.75,0:11:01.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,諦めないと言ったって
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.92,0:11:01.42,default,,0,0,0,,Just because you \Ndon't want to give up?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.62,0:11:04.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どう考えたって 生還なんて
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.80,0:11:04.22,default,,0,0,0,,This is not how \Nyou should survive...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.86,0:11:08.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,へへへ それが
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.86,0:11:08.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうでもねえのさ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.25,0:11:08.34,default,,0,0,0,,You are wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.63,0:11:10.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,奴が口にしてただろ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.68,0:11:10.23,default,,0,0,0,,He was talking about it,\Nwasn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.60,0:11:13.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ここから引き上げてもらおうと
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.60,0:11:13.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,思ったら
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.78,0:11:13.62,default,,0,0,0,,If you want to be saved\Nfrom here,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.47,0:11:16.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺みたいに金を抱いて墜ちるか
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.62,0:11:16.36,default,,0,0,0,,either be like me and come here \Nholding on to money,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.31,0:11:19.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,シャバに強力なお宝でも
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.31,0:11:19.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,隠しておいて
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.36,0:11:19.54,default,,0,0,0,,or hide something valuable \Nin the outside world...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.51,0:11:23.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,助けざるを得ないという
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.51,0:11:23.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,状況しかない
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.54,0:11:23.02,default,,0,0,0,,That's the only way to make sure \Nthat you'll be saved.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.38,0:11:26.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,奴が大事に抱えていた
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.38,0:11:26.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの大金は
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.49,0:11:26.01,default,,0,0,0,,The treasure that he was \Ntaking good care of...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.73,0:11:28.24,default,,0,0,0,,...is cash.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.85,0:11:29.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そういう意味の金
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.25,0:11:35.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だとすると足りないよな かなり
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.34,0:11:34.58,default,,0,0,0,,Which is far \Nfrom enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.12,0:11:37.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だって
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.58,0:11:39.35,default,,0,0,0,,The cash that \Nhe was holding on to...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.49,0:11:41.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,奴が持っていた金は
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.49,0:11:41.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,せいぜい700～800万
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.35,0:11:40.72,default,,0,0,0,,...was at most 7-8 million.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.10,0:11:45.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これじゃあ星３つ使って
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.10,0:11:45.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,救い出す価値なんてない
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.11,0:11:44.33,default,,0,0,0,,It's not worth using \N3 stars to save him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.03,0:11:47.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１つ500万で
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.03,0:11:47.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,取り引きされてるんだから
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.20,0:11:47.99,default,,0,0,0,,Since each star is \Nbeing traded for 5 million,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.87,0:11:51.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,最低 1500万は抱いて
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.87,0:11:51.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,墜ちなきゃ救われない
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.99,0:11:51.33,default,,0,0,0,,he had to be holding\Nat least 15 million.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.71,0:11:55.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,てことは もう１つの保証
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.77,0:11:54.74,default,,0,0,0,,This means that he has\Nanother guarantee.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.04,0:11:57.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,シャバに隠しておいたお宝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.14,0:12:00.34,default,,0,0,0,,He's hidden a great treasure worth\Ntens of millions out there...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.61,0:12:00.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うん千万って額は
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.61,0:12:00.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,くだらない大金
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.65,0:12:04.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そのありかを
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.65,0:12:04.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,岡林だけが知っている
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.68,0:12:03.48,default,,0,0,0,,And only Okabayashi \Nknows where it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.42,0:12:07.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だが仲間に隠し場所が
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.42,0:12:07.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,バレちまったら それまで
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.62,0:12:07.60,default,,0,0,0,,But, if the place was known,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.42,0:12:10.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっさり裏切られる
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.60,0:12:09.24,default,,0,0,0,,he would be easily betrayed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.19,0:12:15.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,100パーセント 仲間にバレぬよう
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.19,0:12:15.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,現金を隠しきるのは難しい
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.38,0:12:12.23,default,,0,0,0,,It's hard to \Nhide cash without...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.23,0:12:14.92,default,,0,0,0,,...letting your comrades \Nknow where it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.70,0:12:18.32,default,,0,0,0,,Which means that\Nthe safest way...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.73,0:12:18.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,となると 一番安心なのは
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.63,0:12:21.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そのお宝を手に墜ちることだ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.69,0:12:21.06,default,,0,0,0,,...is to bring it with you\Nwhen you come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.84,0:12:24.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,つまり うん千万っていう現金を
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.89,0:12:27.00,default,,0,0,0,,In other words, he converted the\Nmoney into precious jewels.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.44,0:12:27.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,小さな宝石とか貴金属に換え
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.21,0:12:30.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それを手に墜ちるしかない
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.24,0:12:29.07,default,,0,0,0,,He had to do that \Nwhen he came here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.19,0:12:31.30,default,,0,0,0,,But still...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.41,0:12:34.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,でも私たちは その…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.48,0:12:34.10,default,,0,0,0,,We are... well... \Nas you can see,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.05,0:12:36.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,このとおり 丸裸で
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.10,0:12:36.55,default,,0,0,0,,we're naked...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.52,0:12:40.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,石田さん 覚えてるか？これ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.55,0:12:39.95,default,,0,0,0,,Ishida... \NDo you remember this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.19,0:12:42.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うっ それって…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.95,0:12:42.35,default,,0,0,0,,Does that mean...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.73,0:12:43.75,default,,0,0,0,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.73,0:12:47.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうさ 奴の背中のばんそうこう
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.56,0:12:46.87,default,,0,0,0,,The bandage on his back!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.20,0:12:51.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,じゃあ まさか…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.24,0:12:51.63,default,,0,0,0,,Then, don't tell me that...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.50,0:12:54.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おい 例のやつ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.29,0:12:55.29,default,,0,0,0,,- Where is it?\N- Yeah, it's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.00,0:12:56.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ ここにあるぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.00,0:12:56.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おい ないぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.29,0:12:56.57,default,,0,0,0,,Hey! It's gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.84,0:13:04.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ざわ… ざわ…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.65,0:13:08.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうさ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.75,0:13:05.77,default,,0,0,0,,That's right...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.45,0:13:11.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今頃 気づいたか まぬけめ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.55,0:13:11.37,default,,0,0,0,,You've noticed it only now, \Nyou blockhead?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.78,0:13:16.78,default,,0,0,0,,Who's the one not paying\Nattention now? Okabayashi! Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.79,0:13:14.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ぬけてんのは貴様なんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.39,0:13:16.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大甘さ バカめ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.34,0:13:33.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,貴様 貴様 貴様！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.44,0:13:33.45,default,,0,0,0,,Darn it! Darn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.24,0:13:35.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何だ これは
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.24,0:13:35.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どういうことだ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.45,0:13:35.43,default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?! \NWhat's the meaning of this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.64,0:13:38.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ど… ど どうって…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.74,0:13:37.50,default,,0,0,0,,Well, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.88,0:13:43.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,このバカ カス ゴミ クズ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.88,0:13:43.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こいつ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.99,0:13:42.94,default,,0,0,0,,You idiot! You piece of trash! \NGarbage! Useless!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.55,0:13:46.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジくん
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.88,0:13:45.68,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.40,0:13:47.81,default,,0,0,0,,Hey, save me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.42,0:13:51.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さあ 救え　この宝石に
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.42,0:13:51.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,1500万以上の価値があるなら
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.44,0:13:51.78,default,,0,0,0,,If these are worth \N15 million or more,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.69,0:13:53.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,救わざるを得まい
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.78,0:13:53.52,default,,0,0,0,,you'll have to save me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.70,0:13:58.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さっさと救え ゴミども
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.84,0:13:55.99,default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and save me, \Nyou pieces of trash!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.47,0:14:02.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,星 売買の残り時間 ３分
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.62,0:14:01.32,default,,0,0,0,,3 minutes left for \Nthe trading of stars!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.24,0:14:10.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,結局 岡林たちのグループは
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.24,0:14:10.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかたなくカイジを指名
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.37,0:14:08.02,default,,0,0,0,,Finally,\NOkabayashi and gang...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.02,0:14:10.11,default,,0,0,0,,...had no choice \Nbut to select Kaiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.38,0:14:13.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジが どさくさに紛れて
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.38,0:14:13.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,かすめた宝石は
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.41,0:14:13.68,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji had made use of the \Nchaotic situation...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.65,0:14:16.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,2000万の価値があった
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.68,0:14:17.84,default,,0,0,0,,...to grab the jewels that's worth\N20 million to save his life!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.09,0:14:18.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,救わざるを得ない
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.26,0:14:36.36,default,,0,0,0,,See you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.27,0:14:39.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,じゃあな
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.27,0:14:39.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジくん
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.62,0:14:38.21,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.86,0:14:43.76,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.88,0:14:44.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジくん…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.60,0:15:10.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こんなことが…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.60,0:15:10.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こんな逆転が起こるなんて
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.66,0:15:05.39,default,,0,0,0,,How could such a thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.00,0:15:09.12,default,,0,0,0,,How could such \Na reversal happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.67,0:15:14.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こんな地の果ての
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.67,0:15:14.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,穴蔵みたいなところでも
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.68,0:15:14.08,default,,0,0,0,,In a place that's like an abyss,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.54,0:15:18.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こんな逆転が…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.63,0:15:16.76,default,,0,0,0,,he pulled off \Nsuch a reversal...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.45,0:15:21.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,諦めなければ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.68,0:15:20.92,default,,0,0,0,,If I hadn't given up...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.82,0:15:24.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,諦めさえしなければ…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.98,0:15:24.50,default,,0,0,0,,If only I hadn't given up...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.66,0:15:29.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おらおら 700 700
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.74,0:15:29.24,default,,0,0,0,,Come on, come on! \N7 million, 7 million!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.53,0:15:32.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,隠してる金 全部出すんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.66,0:15:32.18,default,,0,0,0,,Hand over all the money\N you're hiding!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.09,0:15:34.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ケチケチしてると買い損ねるぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.18,0:15:33.21,default,,0,0,0,,If you're too stingy,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.21,0:15:34.87,default,,0,0,0,,you'll miss the chance to get one!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.70,0:15:36.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あ 安藤
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.87,0:15:36.61,default,,0,0,0,,A-Ando...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.93,0:15:40.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カ カイジさんが消えた
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.46,0:15:40.33,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji... \Nhe's disappeared...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.75,0:15:42.65,default,,0,0,0,,That's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.80,0:15:44.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんなことあるかよ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.80,0:15:44.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もう望みがないから奥にでも…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.65,0:15:44.86,default,,0,0,0,,He must've lost all hope \Nand went further in...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.21,0:15:50.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ざわ… ざわ… ざわ…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.01,0:15:53.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,バ バカな！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.01,0:15:53.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ど… どうして？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.14,0:15:51.89,default,,0,0,0,,I-Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.20,0:15:52.87,default,,0,0,0,,How did he?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.35,0:15:56.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ！貴様
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.46,0:15:55.71,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji! You!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.04,0:16:18.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ… カ カイジさん
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.04,0:16:18.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そ その…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.56,0:16:18.48,default,,0,0,0,,K-Kaiji! Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.47,0:16:27.72,default,,0,0,0,,Stop, stop it! \NThe devil made me do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.68,0:16:30.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,よして ま 魔が差したんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.68,0:16:30.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ちょっと ほんのちょっとだけ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.91,0:16:30.17,default,,0,0,0,,I lost my senses! Really!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.23,0:16:44.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やめようって
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.23,0:16:44.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,僕はギリギリまで その…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.29,0:16:42.25,default,,0,0,0,,Please stop it. Up till\Nthe last moment, I was...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.03,0:16:46.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,欲かいて
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.03,0:16:46.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺を抹殺しようとした奴が
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.26,0:16:46.96,default,,0,0,0,,You guys tried to kill me\Nfor your greed,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.87,0:16:48.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今さら何を言う
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.96,0:16:48.25,default,,0,0,0,,so what are you talking\Nabout?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.80,0:16:50.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,てめえらみたいな裏切り者の
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.88,0:16:50.59,default,,0,0,0,,I don't talk to betrayers,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.81,0:16:53.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,腐れきった最低な奴とは
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.81,0:16:53.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,口もききたくねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.91,0:16:53.59,default,,0,0,0,,lowlifes that don't deserve to live!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.98,0:16:56.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,黙って今持ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.98,0:16:56.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,薄汚ねえ星と金を
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.04,0:16:56.59,default,,0,0,0,,Shut up and hand over \Nall the dirty money...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.48,0:16:59.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,全部出せ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.59,0:16:57.80,default,,0,0,0,,...and stars that you have!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.10,0:17:00.33,default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Kaiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.38,0:17:03.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジさん
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.38,0:17:03.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,出せ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.92,0:17:02.07,default,,0,0,0,,Hand them over!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.05,0:17:05.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,金もだ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.05,0:17:05.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,全部ですか？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.25,0:17:04.30,default,,0,0,0,,The cash as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.51,0:17:05.72,default,,0,0,0,,All of it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.65,0:17:07.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,当たり前だ！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.72,0:17:07.04,default,,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.89,0:17:09.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジさん ひどいっすよ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.94,0:17:10.07,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji! \NThat's too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.96,0:17:12.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,最後はともかく
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.96,0:17:12.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺たちは途中まで
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.07,0:17:13.84,default,,0,0,0,,Apart from the end,\Nweren't all of us comrades?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.53,0:17:14.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,仲間だったじゃないっすか
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.53,0:17:14.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうっすよ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.84,0:17:14.58,default,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.83,0:17:18.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いわばその金は
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.83,0:17:18.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,みんなで協力してつくった金
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.85,0:17:16.06,default,,0,0,0,,So that money...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.06,0:17:18.21,default,,0,0,0,,...was due to everyone's effort!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.47,0:17:20.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それを全部はひどい
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.51,0:17:20.47,default,,0,0,0,,To hand it all over is\Ntoo much!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.40,0:17:23.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジさんだけ得するなんて
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.40,0:17:23.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうっすよ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.47,0:17:22.24,default,,0,0,0,,Only you will \Nbenefit from this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.24,0:17:23.22,default,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.44,0:17:26.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺らにも取り分くださいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.60,0:17:26.26,default,,0,0,0,,Please give us our share as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.82,0:17:37.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いい加減にしろ！ゴミどもが
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.86,0:17:37.00,default,,0,0,0,,That's enough, \Nyou pieces of trash!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.12,0:17:40.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,捨ててやる こんな金
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.12,0:17:40.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,す 捨てるって？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.19,0:17:38.60,default,,0,0,0,,I'll throw this money away!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.55,0:17:40.60,default,,0,0,0,,Throw away...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.82,0:17:44.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うんざりだ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.82,0:17:44.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もううんざりだ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.95,0:17:42.34,default,,0,0,0,,I've had enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.62,0:17:44.07,default,,0,0,0,,I've had more \Nthan enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.03,0:17:49.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うんざりだ うんざりだ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.03,0:17:49.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ヘドが出る
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.35,0:17:47.59,default,,0,0,0,,I've had enough! Enough! \NI want to throw up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.67,0:17:56.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,売って 売ってくれ！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.73,0:17:55.71,default,,0,0,0,,Sell it to me! \NSell it to me please!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.80,0:17:58.68,default,,0,0,0,,I only have 4 million now,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.94,0:17:59.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今は400しかないけど
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.94,0:17:59.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,船から降りたら
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.68,0:18:01.86,default,,0,0,0,,but I'll definitely pay you\Nanother 3 million later!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.61,0:18:01.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,必ず300は上乗せするから
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.64,0:18:04.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,バカ野郎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.64,0:18:04.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,信じられるか そんな話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.86,0:18:04.29,default,,0,0,0,,You idiot, how can I\Nbelieve such a thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.29,0:18:07.71,default,,0,0,0,,It's true! Even if I don't have\Nit now, my parents will pay you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.31,0:18:07.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,本当だ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.31,0:18:07.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺に金はなくても親が出す
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.58,0:18:10.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,親が必ず出す
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.58,0:18:10.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんなこと言うなら
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.71,0:18:09.23,default,,0,0,0,,My parents \Nwill surely pay!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.23,0:18:12.53,default,,0,0,0,,If that's the case, my parents\Nwill pay 7 or 8 million too!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.29,0:18:12.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺の親だって出す
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.29,0:18:12.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,700や800万
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.79,0:18:15.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺も
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.79,0:18:15.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺も親が出す
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.81,0:18:15.15,default,,0,0,0,,Me too! \NMy parents will pay!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.50,0:18:24.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,親だと？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.72,0:18:23.04,default,,0,0,0,,Your parents?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.43,0:18:27.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,黙れ！そんなクズに売るな
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.63,0:18:27.28,default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! \NDon't sell it to them!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.97,0:18:30.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,キャッシュで800万
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.97,0:18:30.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺が買う
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.08,0:18:30.28,default,,0,0,0,,8 million in cash! \NI'll buy it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.41,0:18:33.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カ カイジさん
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.41,0:18:33.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何をバカなことを
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.56,0:18:33.46,default,,0,0,0,,K-Kaiji?! How can you do\Nsuch a stupid thing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.31,0:18:35.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今さら星を買っても
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.46,0:18:35.16,default,,0,0,0,,What's the point \Nof buying stars now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.58,0:18:37.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,売った！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.68,0:18:37.66,default,,0,0,0,,Sold!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.58,0:18:41.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,めちゃくちゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.52,0:18:41.01,default,,0,0,0,,It's all messed up...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.26,0:18:50.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これで あの男を救ってくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.53,0:18:50.07,default,,0,0,0,,I want to use these stars\Nto save that man.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.61,0:19:08.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジくん ありがとう
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.78,0:19:05.99,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.77,0:19:08.17,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.24,0:19:11.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ど どうして こんなおっさんを？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.75,0:19:11.39,default,,0,0,0,,Why him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.45,0:19:13.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,資産でもあるの？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.54,0:19:13.03,default,,0,0,0,,Does he have \Nlots of property?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.38,0:19:17.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ひょっとして こう見えても
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.38,0:19:17.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,シャバにすごい資産が…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.47,0:19:17.03,default,,0,0,0,,Does he have great wealth\Nout there despite his looks?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.03,0:19:18.76,default,,0,0,0,,Idiot, of course he doesn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.05,0:19:19.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,バカ あるわけねえだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.12,0:19:21.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,スカンピンだ 俺たちと同じさ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.25,0:19:21.84,default,,0,0,0,,He's completely broke, \Njust like us!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.72,0:19:24.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジさん 勘弁してくださいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.84,0:19:22.78,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.78,0:19:24.23,default,,0,0,0,,Give us a break!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.19,0:19:26.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それじゃあ…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.19,0:19:26.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,黙れ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.23,0:19:25.00,default,,0,0,0,,Then why?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.30,0:19:26.48,default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.43,0:19:29.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,言ったろ 捨てるって
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.43,0:19:29.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うんざりなんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.48,0:19:29.71,default,,0,0,0,,I said I'd throw it away!\NI've had enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.70,0:19:34.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,損だ 得だ 金だ 資産だ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.70,0:19:34.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんな話はもう
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.71,0:19:32.39,default,,0,0,0,,Losses, gains, \Nmoney, possessions.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.39,0:19:34.35,default,,0,0,0,,I've had enough of that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.27,0:19:37.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんなことを話せば話すほど
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.27,0:19:37.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺たちは あさましく
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.35,0:19:36.41,default,,0,0,0,,The more we talk about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.41,0:19:37.97,default,,0,0,0,,the worse it's going to get.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.84,0:19:40.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,醜く はい回ってることになるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.97,0:19:40.31,default,,0,0,0,,Miserable and unsightly!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.28,0:19:42.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この地獄の釜の底をな
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.31,0:19:42.62,default,,0,0,0,,Here in this insufferable\Nplace!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.62,0:19:44.49,default,,0,0,0,,Don't you understand that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.68,0:19:46.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それが分かんねえのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.06,0:19:49.19,default,,0,0,0,,And the organisers are\Nhaving fun by watching us!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.08,0:19:49.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そして そんな姿を見て
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.08,0:19:49.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,主催者が喜ぶ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.95,0:19:52.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その互いにおとしめ合う
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.95,0:19:52.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,仕組みを考えた
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.99,0:19:52.68,default,,0,0,0,,Those scoundrels\Nare smirking away...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.68,0:19:54.57,default,,0,0,0,,...as we plot \Nagainst each other!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.69,0:19:54.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ブタ野郎がほくそ笑む
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.95,0:19:58.74,default,,0,0,0,,The more we get caught up\Nin winning and losing,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.96,0:19:58.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺たちが損得に振り回されれば
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.96,0:19:58.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,振り回されるほど
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.63,0:20:01.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,血道を上げれば上げるほど
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.74,0:20:00.77,default,,0,0,0,,the more engrossed\Nwe become.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.15,0:20:04.24,default,,0,0,0,,And that's exactly what\Nthose garbage want!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.20,0:20:04.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,結果的に
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.20,0:20:04.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そのゲス野郎の思うつぼ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.24,0:20:08.75,default,,0,0,0,,Don't you feel vexed?!\NDon't you feel vexed?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.40,0:20:09.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,悔しくねえのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.40,0:20:09.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,悔しくねえのかよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.24,0:20:12.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,くそ！くそ くそ くそ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.39,0:20:10.25,default,,0,0,0,,Darn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.70,0:20:13.11,default,,0,0,0,,Darn it, darn it, \Ndarn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.94,0:20:16.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,くそー！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.11,0:20:15.25,default,,0,0,0,,Darn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.33,0:20:18.62,default,,0,0,0,,Darn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.38,0:20:20.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,くそ くそー！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.08,0:20:22.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ くそー！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.67,0:20:21.99,default,,0,0,0,,Darn it!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.66,0:20:29.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,楽しい
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.67,0:20:28.77,default,,0,0,0,,This is enjoyable...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.12,0:20:34.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いや 楽しめそうな男じゃないか
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.19,0:20:32.63,default,,0,0,0,,No, it seems like \NI can get a lot of...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.63,0:20:34.91,default,,0,0,0,,...enjoyment from this man.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.52,0:20:40.28,default,,0,0,0,,Darn it! Darn it! \NDarn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.53,0:20:40.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,くそ くそ くそ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.44,0:20:43.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,くそ野郎！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.53,0:20:42.78,default,,0,0,0,,Darn it!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.18,0:20:51.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こうしてカイジたちの長い夜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.41,0:20:51.43,default,,0,0,0,,With the end of 4 hours\Nof plots and schemes,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.43,0:20:55.79,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji's long night finally\Ndraws to a close.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.45,0:20:56.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,狂気と策略が交差する
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.45,0:20:56.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,４時間あまりが終わった
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.28,0:20:59.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,参加者103名のうち 36名が
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.34,0:20:59.69,default,,0,0,0,,36 out of the 103 participants\Non board the Espoir...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.62,0:21:03.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,エスポワールにのみ込まれ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.62,0:21:03.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,地獄へ墜ちた
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.69,0:21:03.12,default,,0,0,0,,...didn't make the cut and\Nwere met with a cruel fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.49,0:21:08.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そして かろうじて
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.49,0:21:08.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,生還できた者は67名
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.52,0:21:08.16,default,,0,0,0,,And only 67 barely\Nmade it out alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.40,0:21:12.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかし その多くはシャバの借金は
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.40,0:21:12.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,チャラになったものの
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.58,0:21:10.47,default,,0,0,0,,Although most of them \Nhad their debts...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.47,0:21:12.81,default,,0,0,0,,...from the outside world erased,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.97,0:21:15.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,船で また新たな借金を背負い
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.01,0:21:15.69,default,,0,0,0,,they incurred fresh debts \Nfrom the ship,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.50,0:21:18.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,街へ戻ることになる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.69,0:21:17.84,default,,0,0,0,,and returned to the streets...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.32,0:22:35.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ざわ… ざわ…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.82,0:22:43.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ざわ…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.56,0:22:46.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,次回 ｢使者｣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.56,0:22:46.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ざわ…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.66,0:22:45.81,default,,0,0,0,,Next, Messenger.
